OL,4,CEducation secretary promises masks in
OL,5,Cschool will go 'as soon as possible'
OL,6, Scotland's education secretary has
OL,7, promised face coverings in classrooms
OL,8, will be dropped "as soon as possible".
OL,10,FAs most pupils return this week, the
OL,11,Fneed for masks in high schools is one
OL,12,Fof the main mitigations remaining.
OL,14,FThe Scottish government had said the
OL,15,Frequirement would be in place for "at
OL,16,Fleast six weeks", but Shirley-Anne
OL,17,FSomerville told the BBC if it could be
OL,18,Fdropped earlier, it would.
OL,20,FAll secondary pupils must continue to
OL,21,Fwear them at all times.
